{"tid":1795163,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"林兆波唔肯食餃子 - 陳也","createTime":"2019-12-23T16:23:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-05T06:46:27.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"d87a3ba2083fe33d6cf8a01780c1d7bc9efe05be","tid":1795163,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T16:23:06.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E9%99%B3%E4%B9%9F/daily/article/20191223/20829919/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E9%2599%25B3%25E4%25B9%259F%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20191223%2F20829919%2F&d=IuE3y9gLaM%2BC%2BJZgSaDlpv7c%2B9HD3JYLAdxAiSxEDXo%3D&h=95f798c0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E9%2599%25B3%25E4%25B9%259F%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20191223%2F20829919%2F&h=142c1534\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E9%99%B3%E4%B9%9F/daily/article/20191223/20829919/</a><br />\n<br />\n林兆波唔肯食餃子 - 陳也<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20191223/large/1577000326_a532.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20191223%2Flarge%2F1577000326_a532.jpg&h=416929fa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n互聯網<br />\n<br />\n楊天命預測，未來好多高官走佬，將會好大變化。明年三月，香港有個人出現，這個人好犀利，到時有可能變天。<br />\n<br />\n半信半疑之際，澳門傳來動畫，全部契弟迎合甴總歌唱祖國時拍爛手掌千人一面的畫像中，一夫當關的林兆波兄，遺世獨立左手緊按右手。手，唔係用來拍馬屁嘅。握完甴總的手，波兄死命按着滲透全身火燒感那個Pepe冏樣，令網民起哄，封林兆波做前線手足。高調表態不合作勁勇武啊，拒絕行埋的波兄，極可能是楊天命預言三月變天的關鍵。<br />\n<br />\n有五五波機會成為真命天子，波兄身邊的林奠，拍住手歌唱但明顯已經睄到枕邊人「不按本子辦事」。鏡頭捕捉到，林奠那副尊容，難頂過後母。家不和，萬事難興，內外交困的林奠，過唔到人間三月天，一點唔奇。<br />\n<br />\n林兆波罷拍賀馬交，老婆同是姓奠的潘某假如站在前排，會露出柒樣嗎？直送國家首都，強制「食餃子」，是甴總明年整治香港高官上演插翼難飛重頭戲的吉時。高官爭住跳船的海難畫面， 有人已預先鼓掌。 <br />\n<br />\n陳也<br />\n電郵 :mcwriter@appledaily.com"},{"pid":"3343f950924e6477941961211fbe602a15975924","tid":1795163,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T16:23:59.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: orange;\">X&rsquo;MAS EVE 願平安歸香港🇭🇰</span><br />\n日期 : 12月24日 (二)<br />\n時間：19:00 - 22:00<br />\n地點：<br />\n元朗yoho<br />\n沙田 新城市<br />\n尖沙咀 海港城<br />\n旺角 朗豪坊<br />\n銅鑼灣 時代廣場<br />\nLink : @xmasevehkchannel"},{"pid":"fe386c1344a6c434333cbd4216a8a4748b9db0ba","tid":1795163,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T16:26:33.000Z","msg":"怕食到伯邑考<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"edc5e271adcd6a1feaab60784a9c4a78256952e4","tid":1795163,"uid":199739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T05:38:00.000Z","msg":"咩係食餃子"},{"pid":"7a192a95671cbc6fd089b8ecdefa78574bd214a7","tid":1795163,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"edc5e271adcd6a1feaab60784a9c4a78256952e4","tid":1795163,"uid":199739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T05:38:00.000Z","msg":"咩係食餃子"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T05:44:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.hkfilmblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/image79.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkfilmblog.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2014%2F11%2Fimage79.jpg&h=2e6b1bb8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"caa9821ba4d38467cb8008fc5d95efee684a8c4c","tid":1795163,"uid":199739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7a192a95671cbc6fd089b8ecdefa78574bd214a7","tid":1795163,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"edc5e271adcd6a1feaab60784a9c4a78256952e4","tid":1795163,"uid":199739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T05:38:00.000Z","msg":"咩係食餃子"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T05:44:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.hkfilmblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/image79.jpg\" data-thumbnai